 a fundamental institution - the family - over several generations.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aFilm and Media Studies 2019. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aFrench society.  aMaurice Pialat.  aThird Republic.  adirector.  afamily.  afilmmaker.  ala France profonde.  amontage.  apost New Wave.  arealism.1 aWarehime, Marja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978184779437640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781847794376423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781847794376/original  a978-3-11-128363-0  Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles